details.name: HIT Fastest Bike Parkour
details.creator: -Hitokiri-
details.desc: Point to point race with the criss-crossing up the wazoo that features a lot of original sections & new stunt elements such as, the first moving ramps in GTA & a bunch of other cool stuff. ''Agile bikes'' perform the best, however if u decide to pick Faggio, it's probably time to face the cruel reality - you are a damn idiot and ur mom is lying to you when she says that you are a bright kid, don't listen to her.    Word Record - 02.57 by Asudora.
